---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import ThinnerContent from "../../components/ThinnerContent.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import wellness from "../../assets/wellness.png";
import Back from "../../components/Back.astro";

const title = "Wellness Medical Center";
---

<Base title="Wellness Medical Center">
  <ThinnerContent>
    <section class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl sm:text-5xl my-8">{title}</h1>
      <a href="https://wellnessmedicalcenter.com/" target="_blank">
        <Image src={wellness} alt="Wellness Medical Center" class="mb-8 rounded-lg" />
      </a>
      <p class="mb-6">
        <a
          href="https://wellnessmedicalcenter.com/"
          target="_blank"
          class="text-violet-800 hover:text-violet-900 underline transition-colors"
        >Wellness Medical Center</a> is a comprehensive healthcare website I designed and developed from the ground up. The site serves as both an informational resource for patients and a fully functional e-commerce storefront.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6">
        I built the site using the Astro framework and Tailwind CSS. The site integrates with Fullscript for affiliate e-commerce and Jane App for scheduling and patient management. The project also included setting up and designing a blog to support content marketing and patient education.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6">
        The design focuses on accessibility, trust, and ease of navigation—essential qualities for a healthcare website. From the clean visual hierarchy to the intuitive checkout flow, every element was crafted to serve both the practice&rsquo;s brand and their patients&rsquo; needs.
      </p>
    </section>
    <Back next="/work/coastal" />
  </ThinnerContent>
</Base>
